Package grafioschtrader.gtnet.m2m.model

Class InstrumentPriceDTO

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.gtnet.m2m.model.InstrumentPriceDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class InstrumentPriceDTO extends Object implements Serializable
DTO for intraday price data of a single instrument in GTNet M2M communication. Used in both request (with current timestamps) and response (with updated prices). Instrument identification: - Security: isin + currency (toCurrency is null) - Currency pair: currency (fromCurrency) + toCurrency (isin is null)
